[Amit Varma]: called Two Rays of Fallen People, the publisher just sent it to me. So I must read it and

05:08:42.480 --> 05:08:47.560
[Amit Varma]: invite him on the show as well. And, you know, I mean, I love this country as much as you

05:08:47.560 --> 05:08:51.840
[Amit Varma]: do. That's why I, that's why we must fight for it. But I don't want to be Vishwa Guru.

05:08:51.840 --> 05:08:57.760
[Amit Varma]: I want to be Vishwa Bandhu. I think, you know, male ego is the end of everything. So, Karthik,

