[Amit Varma]: like awed by, you know, you're using my episodes as footnotes in your conversation with me.

05:09:08.440 --> 05:09:14.120
[Amit Varma]: It's quite mind blowing. I'm, you know, I'm going to dream about this. So thanks for coming

